   <text:p text:style-name="P7"> Ia s vd, spuse Addison, scoindu-<text:span text:style-name="T1"></text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T1">ceasul. </text:span>Cred c <text:s text:c="2"/>n-ai nimic mpotriv dac ne <text:span text:style-name="T1"></text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T1"></text:span>lni<text:span text:style-name="T1">m</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">cu </text:span>civa din oamenii notri <text:s text:c="2"/>importani... <text:span text:style-name="T1">avem </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">la </text:span>clubul <text:span text:style-name="T2">Union League </text:span>o sal, sus, unde ne d<text:span text:style-name="T1">ucem</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">din </text:span>cnd n cnd <text:s text:c="2"/>s lum masa. Dac-i face p<text:span text:style-name="T1">lcere, <text:s/>a</text:span> vrea s vii cu mine acolo la ora unu. G<text:span text:style-name="T1">sim cu </text:span><text:s text:c="3"/>siguran civa dintre ei  un avocat de-ai notri<text:span text:style-name="T1">,</text:span> ceva oameni de <text:s text:c="2"/>afaceri, judectori...</text:p>
