   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Din pcate, Aileen nu se comporta niciodat cu<text:span text:style-name="T16"> </text:span>dezinvoltura caracteristic femeilor din lumea bun. Nu era niciodat<text:span text:style-name="T16"> </text:span>stp<text:span text:style-name="T16"></text:span>n pe situaie, ci dimpotriv, se lsa dominat de ea. O salva<text:span text:style-name="T16"> </text:span>totdeauna calmul superior i afabilitatea lui Cowperwood. L<text:span text:style-name="T16"></text:span>ng<text:span text:style-name="T16"></text:span> el se<text:span text:style-name="T16"> </text:span>simea o adevrat doamn, oriunde la ea acas. Lsat singur, ns,<text:span text:style-name="T16"> </text:span>oric<text:span text:style-name="T16"></text:span>t ar i fost de mare, curajul ei ncepea s se clatine. Nici un<text:span text:style-name="T16"> </text:span>moment nu-i putea uita trecutul. </text:p>
