   <text:p text:style-name="P13">Printre primii sosii fur doamna Webster Ista doamna Bradford Canda i<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>doamna Walter pl Cotton, care trebui<text:span text:style-name="T18">a</text:span>u s primeasc musafirii mpreu<text:span text:style-name="T18">n </text:span>cu Aileen. Aceste doamne nu-i ddeau <text:span text:style-name="T18">s</text:span>eama<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T18">c</text:span> riscau astfel s-i<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>compromit reputaia pe<text:span text:style-name="T18">entru</text:span> lipsa lor de perspicacitate i exigen;<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>fusese mbtate de luxul afiat de Aileen, de succesu<text:span text:style-name="T18">l</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T18">din</text:span> ce n ce mai<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>mare al lui Cowperwood n lumea fina<text:span text:style-name="T18">n</text:span>elor i de arta, rafinat care<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>domnea, n noua loc<text:span text:style-name="T18">u</text:span>in<text:span text:style-name="T18">.</text:span> Gura doamnei Webster Isra<text:span text:style-name="T18">e</text:span>ls avea <text:span text:style-name="T18">o</text:span> form<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>a<text:span text:style-name="T18">tt</text:span> de caracteristic, nc<text:span text:style-name="T18">t</text:span> ntotdeauna o fcea pe Aileen, de cte<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>ori o vedea, s se g<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>ndeasc la un pete; totui nu era o fiin chiar<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>at<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>t de searbd i <text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>n ziua aceea fusese vioaie i chiar atrgtoare.<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>Doamna Bradford Canda, a crei rochie <text:span text:style-name="T2">vi</text:span><text:span t