   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">fur prezentai. Strzile laterale i piaeta din faa cldirii erau<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>ticsite de trsuri elegante cu cai nrvai. Prietenii intimi au venit<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>mai devreme i <text:soft-page-break/>g<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>sind plcut atmos<text:span text:style-name="T18">f</text:span>era au rmas pn mai trziu.<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>Restauratorul Kinsley adusese o adevrat, armat de che<text:span text:style-name="T18">l</text:span>neri<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>stilai, aliniai ca soldaii sub supravegherea atent a majordomului<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>casei. Sufrageria era lu<text:span text:style-name="T18">x</text:span>os decorat n culori pompeiene, iar risipa de<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>cristaluri i ddea o strlucire superb. Bufetul incrcat cu bunti<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>era aranjat cu mare art. Rochiile de dup mas ale doamnelor aveau<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>culorile toamnei i variau de la gri la purpuriu, maron i verde,<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>armonizindu-se cu pereii de nuan castanie ai holului de la intrare,<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>cu griul nchis i auriul salonului principal, cu roul roman din<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>sufragerie, cu albul i auriul slii de concert i cu culoarea<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>neutr, sepia, a pereilor din galeria de tablouri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">Cowperwood se retrsese cu brbaii n sufragerie, birou i galeria de<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>pictur, iar Aileen, ncurajat de puternica personalitate a soului<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>ei, trona n <text:span text:style-name="T18">v</text:span>anitatea, <text:span text:style-name="T18">f</text:span>rumuseii<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>ei  spectacol demn de a <text:span text:style-name="T18">f</text:span>i<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>privit, aproape nduio<text:span text:style-name="T18">tor,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>ntruchiparea deertciunii aparenelor<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>pieritoare, i<text:span text:style-name="T18">ro</text:span>nia, avuiei i n acelai timp<text:span text:style-name="T18"> amgirea</text:span> ei<text:span text:style-name="T18">. Ac</text:span>east mulime care se perinda prin <text:span text:style-name="T18">salonul soilor Cowperwood</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T18">veni</text:span>se mai mult din<text:span text:style-name="T18"> curiozitate dect din bune inten</text:span>ii, mai mult din<text:span text:style-name="T18"> i</text:span>nvidie dec<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>t din simpatie, <text:span text:style-name="T18">gata s cleveteasc fr pic </text:span>de nelegere; <text:span text:style-name="T18">venise numai s critice.</text:span></text:p>
