   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Doamna Simms, Batisfcut de efectul pro<text:span text:style-name="T18">dus,</text:span> trecu vesel mai departe,<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>nsoit de un t<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>nr ar<text:span text:style-name="T18">tist</text:span> care o urma pas cu pas.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Acest mi<text:span text:style-name="T18">c</text:span> incident i altele asemntoare o f<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>cur<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span> pe Aileen s-i<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>dea seama c<text:span text:style-name="T18">t</text:span> de puin fcea parte din cercul select al oraului, care<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>deocamdat nu-<text:span text:style-name="T18">l</text:span> acceptase nici pe ea, nici pe soul ei. Aproape c <text:span text:style-name="T18">o </text:span>ura pe plicticoasa doamn Israels, care fusese ma<text:span text:style-name="T18">r</text:span>tor la ieirea<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>doamnei Simms; i totui, poziia <text:soft-page-break/>doamnei Isra<text:span text:style-name="T18">el</text:span>s era mai solid dec<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="T18"> a</text:span> altora  c<text:span text:style-name="T18">a</text:span> prob c p<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>n i doamna <text:span text:style-name="T18">S</text:span>imms <text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>i acordase u<text:span text:style-name="T18">n</text:span> Ce mai<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>faci convenional.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">Apariia soilor Addison, Sledd, Kingsland, <text:span text:style-name="T18">Hoeck</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T18">e</text:span>ma i alii<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>nu reui<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>s-o liniteasc. Totui, <text:span text:style-name="T18">du</text:span>p <text:span text:style-name="T18">s</text:span>upeu, tineretul ndemnat de M<text:span text:style-name="T18">c</text:span>Kibben,<text:span text:style-name="T18"> un specialist n misterele i subtilitile promenadei, avu plcerea s-o conduc n acest cortegiu geeric, urmat de </text:span>Cowperwood care-i o<text:span text:style-name="T18">f</text:span>eri<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>braul doamnei Simms. Aileen, ntr-o rochie de saten alb cu puin<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>argint din loc n loc, i cu un colier, brri, cercei i diadem de<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>briliante, avea strlucirea unei prinese orientale. Exulta de<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>fericire, M<text:span text:style-name="T18">cKibben, </text:span>foarte curtenitor, era aproape amoreza<text:span text:style-name="T18">t de ea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13"> E o plcere s danseze omul cu dumneata;<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>i opti admirativ. Esti at<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>t de fr<text:span text:style-name="T18">u</text:span>modaca te mai uiti la ceva ce straluceste intri in contact cu mine ca e singura careas<text:span text:style-name="T18">..</text:span>. un <text:span text:style-name="T18">vis!</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13"> Un vi<text:span text:style-name="T18">s</text:span> cam solid,<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>replic Aileen<text:span text:style-name="T18">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13"> A i fericit s-mi po<text:span text:style-name="T18">t</text:span> da <text:span text:style-name="T18">seama, spuse el, rznd, iar </text:span>Aileen, care n<text:span text:style-name="T18">elesese</text:span> aluzia, <text:span text:style-name="T18">schi un zmbet <text:s/></text:span>galnic. Doamnei <text:span text:style-name="T18">Simms</text:span>, ocupat cu <text:span text:style-name="T18">Cowperwood, </text:span>i scp, spre marele ei regret, <text:span text:style-name="T18">o</text:span> parte <text:span text:style-name="T18">din conversaie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">Dup promendad, Aileen, asalta<text:span text:style-name="T18">t</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T18">de un g</text:span>rup zgomotos de tineri veseli i<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>ndrznei, <text:span text:style-name="T18">i cond</text:span>use<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>s-i vad portretul. Invitaii cu gusturi <text:span text:style-name="T18">con</text:span>venionale, sub influena<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>buturilor, comenta<text:span text:style-name="T18">u</text:span> tabloul lui G<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T17"></text:span>me reprezent<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>nd nuduri imp<text:span text:style-name="T18">udice de</text:span> la un<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>capt al galeriei, portretul strlucitor al lui Ail<text:span text:style-name="T18">e</text:span>en, la cellalt<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>capt, i entuziasmul tinerilor pentru gazd. Doamna Rambaud, fr<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>intenii maliioase, atrase atenia brbatului ei asupra poftei de<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>via a doamnei Cowperwood. Doamna Addison, uimit de bogia<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>impresionant a soilor Cowperwood, care depea cu mult <text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>strlucire, dac n<text:span text:style-name="T18">u</text:span> i <text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>n proporii i opulen tot ceea ce realizas<text:span text:style-name="T18">e</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>ei vreodat, i opti brbatului su: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13"> Omul sta trebuie s ctige<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>bani, nu glum<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13"><text:soft-page-break/> Omul sta, drag Ella, e un financiar nnscut,<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>explic Addison, sentenios. Face tranzacii i cu siguran c va<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>ctiga bani muli. Nu tiu dac vor intra vreodat n rndul bunei<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>societi. Dac ar <text:span text:style-name="T18">f</text:span>i singur, da, fr doar i poate. Ea e frumoas,<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>dar m tem c nu e genul de femeie de care are el nevoie. Este<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>aproape prea frumoas. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13"> Aa cred i eu. Mie personal <text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>mi place. Dar<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>mi-e <text:span text:style-name="T18">f</text:span>ric s<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>nu fac gafe. Ar fi pcat. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">Tocmai atunci trecu Aillen<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>prin faa, lor, ncadrat de doi tineri veseli; obrajii i erau<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>mbujorai de plcere, de vorbele mgulitoare pe care i le spuneau. Se<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>ndrepta spre camera de muzic, ce ddea n salon, formnd sala de bal.<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>Strlucirea mulimii n virtejul dansului i lua ochii; parfumul<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>florilor, sunetul muzicii i a vocilor aveau ceva mbttor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13"> De mult<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>n-am mai vzut o femeie aa de frumoas ca doamna Cowperwood, spuse<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>Bradford Canda re<text:span text:style-name="T18">porter</text:span>ului <text:span text:style-name="T18">mon</text:span>den, Horton Biggers. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13"><text:span text:style-name="T18"> Crezi c o s plac </text:span>lumii noastre? ntreb <text:span text:style-name="T18">prudent ziaristul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13"> <text:span text:style-name="T18">E fermectoare, dar m tem c nu e destul de reinut i nici destul de deteapt. Aici ar trebui <text:s/></text:span>un alt gen de femeie  mai serioas. Ea, <text:span text:style-name="T18">e puin </text:span>prea vioaie. Babele<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>astea n-au s se simt<text:span text:style-name="T18"> niciodat </text:span>bine n compania ei. Prea le face <text:span text:style-name="T18">s</text:span> par<text:span text:style-name="T18"> btrne.</text:span> Ar avea mult mai mult succes dac n-ar fi aa tnr <text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>i<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>frumoas.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Exact asta-i i prerea, mea! exclam Bigger<text:span text:style-name="T18">s,</text:span> care n-avea de fapt<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>nici o prere, era incapabil <text:span text:style-name="T18">s</text:span> ajung singur la concluzii att de<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>precise. Acu<text:span text:style-name="T18">m</text:span> adoptase acest punct de vedere pentru c venea de la<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>Brad<text:span text:style-name="T18">ford</text:span> Canda.</text:p>
