   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">A doua zi <text:span text:style-name="T18">d</text:span>iminea, familia Norrie Simms i alte familii discutar, la<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>micul dejun, conseci<text:span text:style-name="T18">ne</text:span>le strdaniei soilor Cowperwood de a fi primii<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>n lumea bun i ansele de reuit sau de nereuit pe care le aveau.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Din pcate, doamna Cowperwood, remarc doamna Simms, e puin<text:span text:style-name="T18"> s</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>ngace. Totul era prea ostentativ. i ce idee s pun portretul ei la<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>un capt al galeriei i tabloul lui G<text:span text:style-name="T18"></text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T17"></text:span>me la cellalt, i pe urm<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>informaia care a aprut astzi n <text:span text:style-name="T2">Press</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">!</text:span> De ce toate astea <text:span text:style-name="T18">? </text:span>Ca i cum<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>ar i face parte din nalta, societate! Doamna Simms era cam suprat<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>c prietenii ei Kent M<text:span text:style-name="T18">c</text:span>Kibben i Taylor Lord se serviser de ea ca g-i<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span>ajute pe <text:span text:style-name="T18">s</text:span>oii Cowperwood.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Dar lumea, cum i s-a prut? ntreb Norrie pe cnd ungea cu unt o</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">feliu de pine<text:span text:style-name="T19">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Evident, o lume care nu reprezint nimic. Noi eram singurele persoane</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">importante i acum mi <text:span text:style-name="T19">p</text:span>are ru c ne-am dus. i cine snt, m rog,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> s</text:span>oii <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>ia Israels sau Hoecksema? Ce oribil femeie<text:span text:style-name="T19">!</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T19">F</text:span>cea aluzie la<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>doamna Hoecksema.) N-am ntilni n viaa mea o femeie aa proast. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Ieri dup mas am yorbit cu Haguenin, de <text:span text:style-name="T19">la</text:span> ziarul <text:span text:style-name="T2">Press</text:span>, zise Norrie.<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Mi-a<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span><text:s/>spu<text:span text:style-name="T19">s</text:span> c nainte de <text:span text:style-name="T19">a </text:span>veni aici Cowperwood dduse <text:span text:style-name="T19">faliment la Phila</text:span>delphia i c<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>avusese o grm<text:span text:style-name="T19">ad de procese. tiai?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> N<text:span text:style-name="T19">u</text:span>, dar doamna Cowperwood pr<text:span text:style-name="T19">etinde</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T19">c</text:span> a cunoscut acolo familiile Drake i<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Walker. <text:span text:style-name="T19">Voiam s</text:span> vorbes<text:span text:style-name="T19">c</text:span> cu Nelly despre asta. ntotude<text:span text:style-name="T19">a</text:span>u<text:span text:style-name="T19">na</text:span> m-am <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>ntrebat de<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>ce au prsit Philadelphia, d<text:span text:style-name="T19">ac l</text:span>e me<text:span text:style-name="T19">r</text:span>gea aa de bine. <text:span text:style-name="T19">D</text:span>e <text:span text:style-name="T19">o</text:span>bicei cnd<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>i m<text:span text:style-name="T19">erge bine ntr-un </text:span>rm<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>i acolo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14">Simms era gelos c<text:span text:style-name="T19">u</text:span> succesul <text:span text:style-name="T19">financiar, din </text:span>c<text:span text:style-name="T19">e</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T19">n ce </text:span>mai mare al lui <text:soft-page-break/>Cowperwood la Chicago. <text:span text:style-name="T19">i </text:span>apoi comportarea lui<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Cowperwood dovedea o mare inteli<text:span text:style-name="T19">g</text:span>en i un mare curaj, i asta de<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>obicei irit pe toat lumea, n afar de cei nvini de soart sau de<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>cei care reuesc n alte domenii. Acum, n sf<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>it, Simms i ddea<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T19">e</text:span>ama c sosise vremea s tie precis i complet cine era i ce fcuse<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Cowperwood. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14">nainte ca situaia monden a soilor Cowperwood s se <text:span text:style-name="T19">fr </text:span>rezolvat ntr-un fel sau altul, se ivi o nou problem, cu siguran<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>mult mai important, dei Aileen, probabil, n-o socotea astfel.<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Relaiile dintre noile i vechile societi de gaz aerian erau puin<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>ncordate.<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Acionarii vechilor societi se simeau stnjenii. Ar <text:span text:style-name="T19">f</text:span>i<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>vrut s tie cine se a<text:span text:style-name="T19">fl</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>n spatele noilor societi, care ameninau s<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>pun mna pe ceea ce ei considerau de mult drept <text:span text:style-name="T19">u</text:span>n bun al lor. n cele<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>din urm, unul din avocaii angajai de <text:span text:style-name="T2">Nor</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T8">t</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">h Ohicago Gas Illuminating</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T8"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">Company</text:span> ca s lupte mpotriva manevrelor lui De Soto Sippens i ale<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>btr<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>nului general Van Sickle, vznd c Consiliul municipal din Lake<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>View acordase un privilegiu noii societi i Curtea de apel era gata<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>s-l susin, recurse la ideea de-a da n judecat Consiliul municipal, nvinuindu-l c protejeaz noua societate i c toi consilierii<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>fuseser mituii. Cu timpul se str<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T19">s</text:span>eser destule dovezi c Duniway,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Jacob Gerecht i alii din Worth Side fuseser cumprai i darea lor<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>n judecat ar i <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>rziat emiterea definitiv a privilegiului,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>oferind astfel vechilor societi rgazul necesar <text:span text:style-name="T19">pentru</text:span> a chibzui<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>ce msuri s ia n viitor. Avocatul, un anume Parsons, urmrise<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>ndeaproape <text:span text:style-name="T19">p</text:span>e Sippens i ale btrinului gene<text:span text:style-name="T19">ral i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T19">ajunsese la c</text:span>oncluzia c ei nu s<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>altceva<text:span text:style-name="T19"> dect nite oameni de paie i c n dosul lor se afla <text:s/></text:span>Cowperwood, adevratul instigator sau<text:span text:style-name="T19">, dac nu </text:span>el, atun<text:span text:style-name="T19">ci</text:span> oamenii pe care-i<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>reprezenta. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14">Parsons se prezent la biroul lui Cow<text:span text:style-name="T19">perwood</text:span> pentru a avea o<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>discuie; nemulumit de <text:span text:style-name="T19">ntreve</text:span>dere, <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>ncepu s fac investigaii n legtur<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>cu<text:span text:style-name="T19"> trecu</text:span>tul lu<text:span text:style-name="T19">i</text:span> Cowperwood i cu oamenii care-l cu<text:span text:style-name="T19">noscu</text:span>ser <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>nainte de a veni la<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Chicago. Toate ace<text:span text:style-name="T19">ste</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T19">cer</text:span>cetri i contramainaii culminar, la <text:span text:style-name="T19">s</text:span>f<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>ritul<text:span text:style-name="T19"> lunii </text:span><text:soft-page-break/>noiembrie, ntr-un proces la <text:span text:style-name="T2">United States Circuit Court</text:span> prin care Frank<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Algernon Cowperwo<text:span text:style-name="T19">od</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T19">Henry</text:span> De Soto Sippens, Judson P. Van Sickle i alii<text:span text:style-name="T19"> erau </text:span>nvinuii de complot mpotriva intereselor unei societi. Acest proces<text:span text:style-name="T19"> f</text:span>u urmat aproape imediat <text:span text:style-name="T19">de </text:span>altele intentate de ctre societile West i<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>South Side pe baza acelorai acuzaii. Numele lui Cowperwood fu<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>pronunat n fiecare din aceste cazuri, fiind considerat ca puterea<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>care conducea din umbr noile societi i uneltea s oblige pe cele<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>vechi s cumpere ac