   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Domnul Schryhart, fire foarte autorita<text:span text:style-name="T19">r</text:span>, nu voia s nvesteasc bani<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>sau s intre ntr-o asociaie n care el s nu aib partea leului.<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>N-ar <text:span text:style-name="T19">f</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T19">o</text:span>nsimit<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>niciodat s intre ntr-o asemenea combinaie<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>dec<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>t cu condiia ca el s fie <text:soft-page-break/>ef. Se hotr<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span> s-l invite pe Cowperwood<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>la biroul su i s discute problema cu el. O puse deci pe secretara,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>lui s-i <text:span text:style-name="T19">s</text:span>crie<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>un bilet prin care, pe un ton superior, l ruga pe<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Cowperwood s vin la biroul su pentru o chestiune important. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Situaia lui Cowperwood n lumea financiar din Chicago era atunci<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>destul de solid, dei personal se mai resimea, nc de pe urma<text:line-break/>atacurilor nverunate venite din toate prile. n astfel de mprej<text:span text:style-name="T19">u</text:span>rri, firea lui <text:span text:style-name="T19">l</text:span> ndemna s manifeste un dispre suveran pentru<text:line-break/>semenii si  pentru cei bogai ca i pentru cei sraci. tia bine c<text:line-break/>Schryart, dei l cunoscuse personal, nu-l bgase p<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>n atunci ni<text:span text:style-name="T19">ci</text:span>odat n seam.</text:p>
