   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">S<text:span text:style-name="T19">c</text:span>hryhart, un om ncrezut i tiranic, fu puin enervat cnd citi<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>scrisoarea. Era ns convins c o ntrevedere cu Cowperwood nu putea s<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>strice, ba, ar fi fost chiar util. i astfel, ntr-o miercuri dup<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>mas, se prezent la Cowperwood, unde fu foarte bine primit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Bun ziua<text:span text:style-name="T19">,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T19">d</text:span>omnule Schryhar<text:span text:style-name="T19">t</text:span>, l nt<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>mpin<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Cowperwood, <text:span text:style-name="T19">n</text:span>tinzndu-i mna, cordial. mi face<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>mare plcere s<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span> te revd. Cred c ne-am mai nt<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>lnit o fat, acum<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>civa ani.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> Da, ntr-adevr<text:span text:style-name="T19">,</text:span> a<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>a cred, replic Schry<text:span text:style-name="T19">h</text:span>art,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>la<text:span text:style-name="T19">t</text:span> n umer<text:span text:style-name="T19">i</text:span> cap ptrat, ochi negri i musta<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>scurt, tot neagr, deasupra gurii expresi<text:span text:style-name="T19">ve i severe.</text:span> Avea nite<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>ochi implacabili i scruttori.<text:span text:style-name="T19"> Am citit </text:span>n ziare, bineneles, dac poi avea n<text:span text:style-name="T19">c</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T19">edere n ce</text:span> scriu ziarele,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>intr <text:span text:style-name="T19">e</text:span>l direct n subiect, <text:span text:style-name="T19">c te intereseaz </text:span>problema gazului a<text:span text:style-name="T19">e</text:span>rian<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>din Ch<text:span text:style-name="T19">icago. E </text:span>adevrat ? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> Nu-i prea bine s pui temei pe ce<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>scrie-n <text:span text:style-name="T19">ziare,</text:span> rosti Cowperwood, amabil. Dar, spune-mi ziare, vrei s tii?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"><text:soft-page-break/> Ei bine, la drept vorbind, relu Schryh<text:span text:style-name="T19">art, </text:span>privindu-l fix<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>pe financiar,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>problema m interesea<text:span text:style-name="T19">z</text:span> i pe mine. Am impresia c ofer<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>un domeniu <text:span text:style-name="T19">avan</text:span>tajos pentru investiii, i diferii reprezentani ai<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>vechilor societi s-au prezentat la mine i <text:span text:style-name="T19">m-au</text:span> rugat s-i ajut<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>n cazul un<text:span text:style-name="T19">e</text:span>i eventuale fuziuni. (Asta n<text:span text:style-name="T19">u</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T19">e</text:span>ra de loc adevrat). M<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>ntrebam pe ce <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>anse de succes te bizui n operaia pe care vrei s-o<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>ntreprinzi. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> N-a vrea s discutm despre acest lucru, zise<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Cowperwood, zmbind, dec<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>t n cazul n care a cunoate mai bine<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>inteniile i relaiile dumit<text:span text:style-name="T19">a</text:span>le. <text:s/>Dup cum neleg, unii acionari ai<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>vechilor societi au apelat la dumneata ca <text:span text:style-name="T19">s</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">-</text:span>i ajui: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> Da,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>exact. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"><text:s/> <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>i ai<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>impresia c i-ai putea convinge s <text:span text:style-name="T19">f</text:span>uzioneze? <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>i pe<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>ce baz? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> O, cred c e foarte si<text:span text:style-name="T19">m</text:span>plu s dai fiecrui acionar<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>do<text:span text:style-name="T19">u</text:span> sau trei aciuni noi pentru fiecare aciune veche. Apoi a<text:span text:style-name="T19">m</text:span> putea<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>alege un singur grup de dire<text:span text:style-name="T19">c</text:span>tori cu birouri comune, am opri toate<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>procesele <text:span text:style-name="T19">i</text:span> toat lumea ar fi mulumit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14">Sc<text:span text:style-name="T19">h</text:span>ryhart era calm i<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>vorbea pe un ton superior, de parc Cowperwood nu s-ar <text:span text:style-name="T19">f</text:span>i gndit cu<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>mult n un la asta; vedea cu uimire c planul <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>ntocmit de el era<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>acu<text:span text:style-name="T19">m</text:span> prezentat de S<text:span text:style-name="T19">c</text:span>hryhart, un om at<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>t de puternic la Chicago, i<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>care pn atunci gsise<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>de<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>cuviin s-l ignoreze.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>n ce condiii, <text:span text:style-name="T19">l</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>ntreb Cowperwood, pre<text:span text:style-name="T19">c</text:span>aut,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>crezi c-ai putea convinge no<text:span text:style-name="T19">i</text:span>le so<text:span text:style-name="T19">c</text:span>ieti s <text:span text:style-name="T19">f</text:span>uzio<text:span text:style-name="T19">n</text:span>eze<text:span text:style-name="T19"> cu cele vechi?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> n aceleai condiii ca pe cele vechi, bin<text:span text:style-name="T19">e</text:span>nele<text:span text:style-name="T19">s</text:span> dac ele nu s-au<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>angajat prea mult. Fire<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>te, n<text:span text:style-name="T19">u</text:span> m-am gndit nc la toate amnuntele.<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Dou sau trei aciuni pentru una veche, proporional cu investiiile.<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Evident, trebuie s <text:span text:style-name="T19">s</text:span>e in seama i de prejudiciile vechilor<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>societi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Cowperwood czu pe g<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>nduri. Nu stia <text:span text:style-name="T19">d</text:span>ac era bine sau ru s primeasc.<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>As<text:span text:style-name="T19">t</text:span>a ar fi fost o ocazie de a vinde tot vechilor societi. Dar n<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>felul acesta <text:soft-page-break/>veniturile vor fi ncasate de Schryhart i nicidecum de<text:span text:style-name="T19"> e</text:span>l. Pe c<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>t vreme dac mai ateapt  chiar dac, Schryhart ajunge s<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>contopeasc cele trei soci<text:span text:style-name="T19">e</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>i vechi  Cowperwood avea anse s<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>impun<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span> condiii mai avantajoase pentru el. Nu prea tia ce s fac.<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>n cele din urm l ntreb:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> C<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>te aciuni ale noii societi ar rm<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>ne n m<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>inile dumitale, sau<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>n minile grupului de directori, dup ce fiecare societate  nou i<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>veche  i va <text:span text:style-name="T19">f</text:span>i primit partea dup sistemul pe care-l preconizezi ?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Cred c treizeci i cinci sau patruzeci la sut din numrul total,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>spuse Sehryhart, insinuant. Ar merita osteneala.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> De acord, ncuviin Cowperwood, cu un z<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>mbet, dar, fiindc eu snt<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>cel care a dat jos fructul din pom, s-ar cdea ca o bun parte din<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>aciuni s mi se lase mie. Ce prere ai?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Ce vrei s spui cu asta?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Exact ce-am spus. Eu personal am organizat noile societi care au<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>fcut posibil fuziunea propus de dumneata. Planul dumitale nu este<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>altceva dec<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>t planul <text:span text:style-name="T19">l</text:span>a care eu lucrez de mult. Directorilor vechilor<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>societi le e ciud pe mine, numai pentru c am intrat n c<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>mpul lor<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>de aciune. Ei, i dac sta este motivul pentru care prefer s<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>lucreze cu dumneata, i nu cu mine, cred c mi se cuvine, n schimb, o<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>parte mult mai mare din aciuni. Eu, personal, n-am investit prea mult<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>n noile societi, snt mai degrab un fel de agent de legtur. (Asta<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>era o minciun, dar Cowperwo<text:span text:style-name="T19">o</text:span>d prefera s-i dea, oaspetelui si t impresie.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Drag domnule Cowperwood, zise Schryhart<text:span text:style-name="T19">,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T19">z</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T19">b</text:span>ind, pare-se uii<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>c eu voi fi acela care va investi aproape tot capi<text:span text:style-name="T19">t</text:span>alul pentru aceast<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>operaie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> <text:span text:style-name="T19">i</text:span> dumneata uii c eu nu snt un naiv. <text:span text:style-name="T19">S</text:span>nt gata s bag toi banii<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>necesari i s-i dau o prim frumoas peniru serviciile dumitale, dac<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>propunerea mea i convine. Uzinele i privilegiile vechilor<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>societi c<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span>t i ale celor noi au oarecare valoare. Nu <text:span text:style-name="T19">u</text:span>ita Chicago este un ora n plin dezvoltare<text:span text:style-name="T19">.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"><text:soft-page-break/> Da, tiu, replic<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Schryhart, evaziv, dar mai tiu i c ai de dat o lupt lung i<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>costisitoare<text:span text:style-name="T19">.</text:span> n condiiile actuale nu poi ajunge la nici un acord cu<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>vechile societi. Dup informaiile mele nu vor s lucreze cu<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>dumneata. Va<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>fi nevoie de o persoan <text:span text:style-name="T19">d</text:span>in<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>a<text:span text:style-name="T19">f</text:span>ar, un om ca mine <text:span text:style-name="T19"> i</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T19">f</text:span>luent, sau, poate, mai bine zis, cu o poziie solid n Chicago.<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Cineva care <text:span text:style-name="T19">s</text:span>-i <text:span text:style-name="T19">c</text:span>unoasc<text:span text:style-name="T19"></text:span> pe toi oamenii acetia i ast<text:span text:style-name="T19">f</text:span>el s<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>nlesneasc fuziunea. Crezi c exist altcineva ma<text:span text:style-name="T19">i</text:span> nimerit ca mine? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> N-ar fi de loc exclus <text:span text:style-name="T19">s</text:span> existe, spuse Co<text:span text:style-name="T19">w</text:span>perwood, foarte<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>degajat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> Nu prea-mi vine s cred<text:span text:style-name="T19">;</text:span> n orice caz <text:span text:style-name="T19">n</text:span>u acum nu n<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>situaia asta. Vechile societi nu snt dispuse s lucreze cu<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>dumneata, cu mine ns vor lucra. Nu preferi s, accepi condiiile<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>mele i s m lai s<text:span text:style-name="T19">-</text:span>i dau drumul i s isprvim? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> Pe baza asta,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>niciodat, replic Cowperwood, simplu. Noi am ptruns prea departe n<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>teritoriul duman, am realizat prea multe. Trei sau patru ac<text:span text:style-name="T19">iuni</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T19">noi </text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>schimbul unei aciuni vechi  i asta <text:span text:style-name="T19">indife</text:span>rent de ce se va <text:span text:style-name="T19">oferi <text:s/></text:span>acionarilor noi. <text:span text:style-name="T19">I</text:span>ar din <text:span text:style-name="T19">ce rmne, mi </text:span>se cuvine o jumtate. Chiar i aa, <text:span text:style-name="T19">mpart cu alii (Nici </text:span>asta nu era adevrat).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> <text:span text:style-name="T19">Nu, se </text:span>mpotrivi Schryhart, evaziv ns ostil,<text:span text:style-name="T19"> i scuturnd </text:span>ndrtni<text:span text:style-name="T19">c</text:span> din cap. Nu se poate. Ris<text:span text:style-name="T19">curile sunt prea mari. A</text:span> ceda poate un sfert  dar<text:span text:style-name="T19"> nc nu tiu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> <text:span text:style-name="T19"><text:s/>O jumtate sau nimic, strui Cowperwood, pe un ton ferm. </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P15">Schryhart se ridic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> Asta-i ul<text:span text:style-name="T19">t</text:span>imul dumitale cuv<text:span text:style-name="T19">nt, nu? ntreb.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> Ultimul! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> Atunci mi-e team, relu<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>Schryhart<text:span text:style-name="T19">, c n</text:span>u ne vom putea nelege<text:span text:style-name="T19">.</text:span> Personal, mi pare ru. Te, ateapt<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>o lupt de lung durat i costisitoare. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14"> De asta nu m-am ndoit<text:span text:style-name="T19"> </text:span>niciodat, r<text:span text:style-name="T19">sp</text:span>unse financiaru<text:span text:style-name="T19">l</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:span text:style-name="Label">Capitolul XII</text:span><text:line-break/>Noi planuri</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Cowperwood, care l nfruntase at<text:span text:style-name="T20"></text:span>t de politicos dar ferm pe<text:span text:style-name="T20"> </text:span>Schryhart, descoperi mai trziu c cine <text:span text:style-name="T20">r</text:span>idic sabia de sabie piere.<text:line-break/>Avocatul su vigilent sttea de gard la Palatul administrativ unde<text:line-break/>con<text:span text:style-name="T20">s</text:span>iliile oreneti i steti, tribunalele i aa mai departe<text:line-break/>emiteau certificate pentru constituirea unor noi societi. Afl repede<text:line-break/>c se pregtea o contraofensiv destul de serioas mpotriva<text:line-break/>iniiativelor luate de Cowperwood. Btr<text:span text:style-name="T20"></text:span>nul general Van Sickle aduse<text:line-break/>primul vestea c se petrecea ceva n legtur cu societatea <text:span text:style-name="T2">Nor</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">t</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">h<text:line-break/>Side</text:span>. Sosi ntr-o dup-mas trziu, cu paltonul lui ponosit, aruncat<text:line-break/>neglijent pe umeri, i cu plria, mic de fetru tras peste ochii cu<text:line-break/>spr<text:span text:style-name="T20"></text:span>ncene stu<text:span text:style-name="T20">f</text:span>oase.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Bun seara, domnule general, Cu ce-a pu<text:span text:style-name="T20">t</text:span>ea s-i fiu de folos? l<text:span text:style-name="T20"> </text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T20"></text:span>mpin Cowperwood.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Btr<text:span text:style-name="T20"></text:span>nul se aez, cu expresia unui om care aduce o veste proast.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Cred c se pregtete o furtun, cpitane, i se adres, el,<text:span text:style-name="T20"> </text:span>ntrebuin<text:span text:style-name="T20"></text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T20">d</text:span> numele pe care obinuise s i-l dea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"> Ce s-a mai ntimplat iar ? ntreb Cowperwood.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P17"> Deocamdat mai nimic, dar s-ar putea s se ntmple. Cineva, nu tiu<text:span text:style-name="T20"> </text:span>nc cine, vrea s uneasc cele trei societi vechi ntr-una singur.<text:span text:style-name="T20"> </text:span>S-a cerut la Springfield o autorizaie pentru constituirea<text:span text:style-name="T20"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">Companiei u</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">i</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">t</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">e de Gaz Aerian i Combustibil din</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">Chicago</text:span> i directorii in edine la <text:span text:style-name="T2">Douglas Trust</text:span>.<text:span text:style-name="T20"> T</text:span>oa<text:span text:style-name="T20">te</text:span> astea le tiu de la Duniway, care s-ar p<text:span text:style-name="T20">rea</text:span> c ar<text:span text:style-name="T20">e</text:span> undeva nite<text:span text:style-name="T20"> </text:span>prieteni informai.</text:p>
